Dates and MySQL Specific Functions
16.
Assuming the Assignments table has a start_date column, find the Employee Name and their oldest project start date.
SELECT Employees.employee_name,
MIN(Assignments.start_date) AS Oldest_Project_Date
FROM Employees
INNER JOIN Assignments
ON Employees.employee_id = Assignments.employee_id
GROUP BY Employees.employee_name;
